{"id": 61315, "date": "2025-11-07T04:00:40", "date_gmt": "2025-11-07T12:00:40", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61315"}, "modified": "2026-06-30T17:30:48", "modified_gmt": "2026-07-01T00:30:48", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-november-7-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/11/07/kingdom-of-days-november-7-2/", "title": {"rendered": "November 7"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Daryl Hall and John Oates open for Bruce and the E Street Band for two shows at Max&#8217;s Kansas City in New York. This is the second of a five-night/ten-show stand.</p>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two nights at Armadillo World Headquarters in Austin.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"13992\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-11-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1974-11-07.jpg?fit=500%2C448&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,448\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-11-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1974-11-07.jpg?fit=500%2C448&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-13992 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1974-11-07.jpg?resize=500%2C448&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"448\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1974-11-07.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/1974-11-07.jpg?resize=300%2C269&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Songwriter Carl D&#8217;Errico (co-writer of &#8220;It&#8217;s My Life,&#8221; which Bruce performed a few days prior at the Palladium, with D&#8217;Errico in attendance) invites Bruce over to his house for dinner. Bruce accepts, dines, and jams with D&#8217;Errico that evening.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"6207\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-1107/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1976-1107.jpg?fit=275%2C183&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"275,183\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-1107\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1976-1107.jpg?fit=275%2C183&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-6207 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1976-1107.jpg?resize=275%2C183&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"275\" height=\"183\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce holds a recording session for\u00a0<em>Darkness on the Edge of Town\u00a0</em>at The Record Plant in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays the first rock concert at Cornell University ever to have reserved seat ticketing. During the show, Bruce debuts his &#8220;I Get Mad&#8221; interlude in &#8220;She&#8217;s the One.&#8221; The sound quality isn&#8217;t great, but you can listen to it below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vbJagljGCSw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22352\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-11-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?fit=1391%2C1402&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1391,1402\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-11-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?fit=758%2C764&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22352 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?resize=758%2C764&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"764\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?w=1391&amp;ssl=1 1391w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?resize=298%2C300&amp;ssl=1 298w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?resize=1016%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1016w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?resize=768%2C774&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1978-11-07.png?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"13994\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/46628013495_ede92039e7_o/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/46628013495_ede92039e7_o.jpg?fit=1250%2C649&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1250,649\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"46628013495_ede92039e7_o\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/46628013495_ede92039e7_o.jpg?fit=758%2C394&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-13994 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/46628013495_ede92039e7_o.jpg?resize=758%2C394&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/46628013495_ede92039e7_o.jpg?w=1250&amp;ssl=1 1250w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/46628013495_ede92039e7_o.jpg?resize=300%2C156&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/46628013495_ede92039e7_o.jpg?resize=768%2C399&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/46628013495_ede92039e7_o.jpg?resize=1024%2C532&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1987:</strong>\u00a0<em>Tunnel of Love\u00a0</em>reaches the Number 1 spot on the album charts in the U.S.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_kzffdY_cJkoCRhUeuDkaEhb5kbWvEC8SU\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2006:\u00a0</strong>Bruce premieres a new arrangement of &#8220;Blinded by the Light&#8221; to open his Seeger Sessions show in Antwerp.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7VTKGHf6OqM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/g6BjFSg3s2M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2007: </strong>At Town Hall in New York City, Bruce supports Stand Up for Heroes, a benefit show for the Bob Woodruff Family Fund, sponsored by the New York Comedy Festival. Bruce plays three acoustic songs and auctions his motorcycle to support the foundation.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QFA1QSoiF6E?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22359\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2007-11-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?fit=1661%2C1015&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1661,1015\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2007-11-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?fit=758%2C463&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22359 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?resize=758%2C463&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"463\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?w=1661&amp;ssl=1 1661w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?resize=300%2C183&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?resize=1024%2C626&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?resize=768%2C469&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2007-11-07.png?resize=1536%2C939&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play the first of two very special full-album shows at Madison Square Garden in New York City. Tonight, Night One, features Bruce&#8217;s first full performance of <em>The Wild, The Innocent &amp; The E Street Shuffle,\u00a0</em>featuring the tour premieres of &#8220;Wild Billy&#8217;s Circus Story&#8221; and &#8220;New York City Serenade.&#8221; The band is joined by full horn and string sections for the occasion, plus Richard Blackwell on conga, and Elvis Costello makes a guest appearance in the encores for &#8220;(Your Love Keeps Lifting Me) Higher and Higher.&#8221; This show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3ajmKLeorXQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/K5zrogkpIgM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PL325295D87B2216EC\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/73iCt0VBVpw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/25vh4ZwloHY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2016: </strong>On Election Eve,\u00a0Bruce supports U.S. presidential candidate Hillary Clinton, performing three acoustic songs at a rally at Independence Hall in Philadelphia.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Jsf5w6w1QSs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22360\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2016-11-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?fit=1787%2C1647&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1787,1647\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2016-11-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?fit=758%2C699&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22360 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?resize=758%2C699&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"699\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?w=1787&amp;ssl=1 1787w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?resize=300%2C276&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?resize=1024%2C944&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?resize=768%2C708&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2016-11-07.png?resize=1536%2C1416&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2018: </strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City. In attendance tonight: John Fogerty.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"13995\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2018-11-07/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2018-11-07.jpg?fit=492%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"492,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1541664917&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2018-11-07\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2018-11-07.jpg?fit=492%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13995\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2018-11-07-295x300.jpg?resize=758%2C768\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2018-11-07.jpg?resize=295%2C300&amp;ssl=1 295w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2018-11-07.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2018-11-07.jpg?w=492&amp;ssl=1 492w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2020:\u00a0</strong>Bruce appears in the introduction video at Jon Landau&#8217;s induction into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame.</p>\n<div id=\"v-0OS8Z512-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/0OS8Z512?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2022:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes his customary appearance at Stand Up For Heroes at David Geffen Hall in New York City. His four-song set features the public debut of &#8220;House of a Thousand Guitars.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" w